# Appendix D: Creature Statistics
Spells [and class features] allow characters to [transform into animals,] summon creatures [to serve as familiars], and create undead. Statistics for such creatures are grouped in this appendix for your convenience. For information on how to read a stat block, see the *Manual of Monsters* or *Monster Manual*.

